<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="hotspotmining" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><ul class="hotspotminingNavbar clearfix">
<li class="active" data-id="306738">TA说</li>
</ul>
<div id="hotspotminingContent-306738" class="hotspotminingContent clearfix showPic" style="display: block">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=4c205afcd0f21134abb51106&fr=qingtian&lemmaId=191597" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=add5058e04fa513d51ff3f9e5b5066cd/c995d143ad4bd1134faa276056afa40f4bfb0578.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=4c205afcd0f21134abb51106&fr=qingtian&lemmaId=191597" target="_blank">中国古人问天的智慧：读懂二十四节气</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2018-04-20 10:04</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>二十四节气作为中国古代农业文明的具体表现，在高速现代化的今天，早已失去了其原有的功能与作用，成为日期上的附注。但“二十四节气”是值得传承发扬的传统文化。</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=4c205afcd0f21134abb51106&fr=qingtian&lemmaId=191597" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
</div>
