<div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
二十四节气
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">外文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
24 solar terms
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">起源年代</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%A4%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3/4298932" data-lemmaid="4298932">上古时代</a>
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">历&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;法</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
干支历
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">划分依据</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
地球在黄道上的位置变化
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">反&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;映</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
地球的回归运动，时节物候的变化
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">起&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;源</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
历法，北斗七星斗柄顶端的指向
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">理论反映</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
太阳周年<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%A7%86%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8/4369485" data-lemmaid="4369485">视运动</a>
</dd>
</dl></div>
